        </header>
        <div id="comment_body_46397091" class="comment-wrapper" data-points="1" data-reason="Normal">
            <div class="comment-body">The attackers moved the BTC balances from the Flexcoin <a href="https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Hot_wallet" title="bitcoin.it">"hot wallet"</a> <span class="domain-text"> [bitcoin.it]</span>  to their own wallets (accounts).  As soon as the bitcoin network validated the transaction, the coins were effectively "spent" - i.e., successfully stolen.</div>
